Selim Nurudeen (amuru 1 Febrụwarị 1983  ) bu onye ihe mgbochi si Naijiria
N'afọ 2010, ọ gbara n'asọmpị Afrịka nke afọ 2010 na Nairobi wee nweta ihe nrite ọla ọcha n'ime ihe mgbochi 110 mita na nkeji 13.83 sekonds
Ọ nọchitere anya Naijiria ugboro abụọ na asọmpi Olympics, na 2008 ya na 2012
Ugbu a ọ na-ejide ndekọ egwuregwu Nigeria n'ime ihe mgbochi 60 mita na oge nke 7.64.
Àtụ:Footer All-Africa Champions 110 m Hurdles Men
